{"tid":741338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「刺客」首在港島犯案　新巴座椅頭枕插兩針","createTime":"2018-07-13T14:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T14:43:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"209c69c28c141d9ecae44b09d87044ca94bcc331","tid":741338,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180713222854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180713222854&h=e9958831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴士放針事件沒完沒了，今午(13日)九巴905號線被放針，有男乘客遭拮傷後，「刺客」竟首次在港島的新巴犯案，晚上7時許，一輛14號線新巴，抵達西灣河太康街38號嘉亨灣巴士總站時，姓楊(33歲)男車長接獲乘客通知，指於上層近尾排近窗口的座椅頭枕邊位置，發現插有2支長約6厘米大頭針。<br />\n<br />\n事件中幸無乘客受傷，楊其後通知站長並報警求助。警員接報到場，經初步調查後，案件列作刑事毀壞，交由東區警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。新巴發言人表示，涉事巴士裝有閉路電視，公司會配合警方調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180713%2Fbkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001.html&d=ceD5UE%2FeaeY398%2BLRcCkabDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=bbebf2c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8447b43e8fb618c9a7b63c014dc3391509e3cb65","tid":741338,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"東方不敗重現江湖"},{"pid":"4ae22c4ae89a400bd130e2541c82a2c8fe81ddbb","tid":741338,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8447b43e8fb618c9a7b63c014dc3391509e3cb65","tid":741338,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"東方不敗重現江湖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"欲練神功"}]}